<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="V" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Vault2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Vault,</orth> vb. to leap, to jump: <cit><quote>--ed into his seat,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 4.1.107" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A IV, 1, 107</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>--ing into my saddle,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h5 5.2.142" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 V, 2, 142</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>--ing ambition,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mac 1.7.27" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. I, 7, 27</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>--ing variable ramps,</quote> <bibl n="shak. cym 1.6.134" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. I, 6, 134</bibl></cit>. cf. <emph>Pretty-vaulting.</emph>
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>